{
  "stem": "12674.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe he looked out for him because he had a personal connection.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, he, he was his house Jew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How do I know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe he had respected him for, for behaving the way he did.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe he respected him from before, and he liked him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he thought, this is not a real Jew because the way he behaves.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He's one of us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He's a good person.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, who knows what goes on in the mind of some-- somebody like that, an abomination like that?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, so he-- all through, through the time that we were in Theresienstadt, we were never on a transport.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they went on all the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- Theresienstadt was only a place-- it was a transshipment point.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People came, and they were sent from there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "People were sent from, from, from, from Vienna, from, from Germany, from Prague, or from Czechoslovakia, from Austria, everywhere to Theresienstadt-- from Holland.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from Theresienstadt, they shipped them east.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Kuchman lost his job in the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the guy that came after him no longer had any interest or wasn't even-- I'm sure he was not aware that our name was never allowed on any list.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when the next-- we knew when he came.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were put on the list, and we had to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When was it?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was in the, the first week of November 1943.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And somebody came to our house at about 9 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he says, you have three hours.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You're in the transport.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we wanted-- it, it was-- [BACKGROUND NOISE] That's downstairs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's Gregory.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I lost my thought.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Edit it out.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
